# 8.1
ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price, colour = cut)) +
  geom_point() +
  xlab("  (carat)") +
  ylab(" (USD)")

# 8.2
# alpha   
ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price, colour = cut)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.25) +
  xlab("  (carat)") +
  ylab(" (USD)")

# 8.3
ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price, colour = cut, shape = cut)) +
  geom_point(size = 1.5) +
  xlab("  (carat)") +
  ylab(" (USD)")
